    "Title": "Secure Bounty: ~mission(TargetName) (VHRT)",
    "Description": "ABOUT THE JOB\nmicroTech Protection Services is looking for a qualified bounty hunter to apprehend ~mission(TargetName) who has so far been able to evade capture. They are coordinating an active raid that has spread throughout ~mission(Location|Address).  \n\nOur hope is that you may be able to finally draw them out of hiding if you confront their forces at several different attack points. With their numbers sufficiently weakened, ~mission(TargetName|Last) will most likely risk exposure and you will be able to confront them directly.\n\nRESPONSIBILITIES\n\u2022 Provide own transportation to ~mission(Location|Address).\n\u2022Confront ~mission(TargetName)\u2019s criminal associates to draw the target into the open.\n\u2022 Neutralize ~mission(TargetName); using force if necessary.\n\nMINIMUM QUALIFICATIONS\n\u2022 Access to combat equipment and mode of transport.\n\u2022 Available for immediate deployment.\n\nPREFERRED QUALIFICATIONS\n\u2022 Ability to handle high pressure situations.",
